- **Calendar:** Only the 10:00 ET prelim UoM Sentiment (consensus 46.1 vs prior 48.2) and Inflation Expectations (prior 4.5%) — both marked **Pending** (not yet released). The real story is next week's **Jun 16–26 convergence**: FOMC + dot plot (Jun 17), Triple Witch + S&P rebalance (Jun 19), Russell reconstitution (Jun 26).
- **Watchlist:** No earnings today. Tier 1 movers RKLB +4.64% (Nasdaq 100 add) and ALB +3.78%. Flagged an oversold nuclear/rare-earth cluster (CEG, CCJ, LYSCF) and extended cyber momentum (FTNT RSI 69).
- **Sectors:** Nuclear and Space led; ORCL -11% is an AI-capex overhang.

